## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="69026-135">当在添加了一系列设计时和运行的时，会自动分配给"Default"<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea>对象或第一个可用的图表区域中<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartAreaCollection>如果"Default"不存在。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69026-135">When a series is added at both design time and run time, it is automatically assigned to the "Default" <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea> object, or the first available chart area in the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartAreaCollection> if "Default" does not exist.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="69026-136">如果不希望绘制数据系列，请将此属性设置为零长度字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69026-136">Set this property to a zero-length string if you do not want the series to be plotted.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```vb  
' Create a new legend and associate three series with the legend.  
Public Sub CreateSecondLegend()  
    ' Attach the first series to a chart area.  
    Chart1.Series["Series1"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 1";  
  
    ' Attach the second series to a chart area.  
    Chart1.Series["Series2"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 2";  
  
End Sub 'CreateSecondLegend  
```  
  
```csharp  
// Create a new legend and associate three series with the legend.  
public void CreateSecondLegend()  
{  
     // Attach the first series to a chart area.  
     Chart1.Series["Series1"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 1";  
  
     // Attach the second series to a chart area.  
     Chart1.Series["Series2"].ChartArea = "Chart Area 2";  
  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="69026-220">获取或设置可以是任何有效的 ARGB （alpha、 红色、 绿色、 蓝色） 值的序列的阴影颜色。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69026-220">Gets or sets the shadow color of a series, which can be to any valid ARGB (alpha, red, green, blue) value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="69026-221">Alpha 值可用来实现逼真的阴影的效果;请尝试使用阴影颜色值为"128,0,0,0"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69026-221">The alpha value can be used to achieve a realistic shadow effect; try using a color value of "128,0,0,0" for shadows.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="69026-222">若要实现阴影，设置<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.ShadowOffset%2A>属性设置为零 (0) 以外的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="69026-222">To implement a shadow, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.ShadowOffset%2A> property to a value other than zero (0).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```  
' Set series shadow color and offset  
Public Sub SetSeriesShadow()  
     Chart1.Series("Default"}.ShadowColor = Color.Blue  
     Chart1.Series("Default"}.ShadowOffset = 2  
End Sub 'SetSeriesShadow  
```  
  
```csharp  
// Set series shadow color and offset   
public void SetSeriesShadow()  
{      
    Chart1.Series("Default"}.ShadowColor = Color.Blue;  
    Chart1.Series["Default"].ShadowOffset = 2;  
}  
```
